# proptest-regressions/ is committed intentionally.
#
# Proptest auto-persists failing seeds here as `proptest_<filename>.txt`
# (e.g. proptest_flags.txt, proptest_math.txt). CI replays persisted
# seeds on every run, so a regression that surfaces locally is
# deterministically caught in CI.
#
# Do NOT add this directory to .gitignore.
# Phase 27 / Plan 27-02 — RESEARCH §Pitfall 1 mitigation.
